$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
add_it

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
add_it -  This method adds a message into all the correct folders and stuff.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void add_it(class mail_message mesg,
int flag)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^mesg%^RESET%^ - the message to send
%^BOLD%^flag%^RESET%^ - if this is set to a non-zero value then no delivery messages will
occur
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/folder_handler.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method adds a message into all the correct folders and stuff.
This is the method that is called when a piece of mail is actually
sent.
.EP

